                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of high-purity ultraviolet calcium fluoride",
                    "一种高纯紫外氟化钙的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a preparation method of high-purity ultraviolet calcium fluoride, which comprises the following steps: an acidolysis process, a primary impurity removal process, a secondary impurity removal process, a double decomposition process, a preparation process and a treatment process: adding an acid solution into calcite mineral powder to obtain a reaction solution, adding hydrogen peroxide into the reaction solution to remove impurity iron, adjusting the pH value by using calcium hydroxide, and performing ultrasonic treatment to obtain high-purity ultraviolet calcium fluoride. Adding an acid solution into the primary impurity-removed solution to adjust the pH value, then adding an ammonium sulfide solution to remove impurities such as iron, heavy metals and rare earth to obtain an impurity-removed calcium solution, and reacting the impurity-removed calcium solution with ammonia water and carbon dioxide gas to obtain wet calcium carbonate; wet calcium carbonate obtained through cleaning reacts with hydrofluoric acid to generate calcium fluoride, high-purity ultraviolet calcium fluoride is obtained through low-temperature vacuum drying, atmospheric sintering, heat preservation and cooling, the calcium fluoride prepared through the method is small in impurity content and high in purity, and the ultraviolet transmittance, the laser damage threshold value, the single crystal caliber value, the birefringence and the like meet the use requirements."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种高纯紫外氟化钙的制备方法，包括以下步骤：酸解工序、一次除杂工序、二次除杂工序、复分解工序、制备工序、处理工序，向方解石矿粉中加入酸溶液得到反应溶液，向反应溶液里加入双氧水除去杂质铁，用氢氧化钙调PH，除去杂质镁，得到一次除杂溶液，向一次除杂溶液中加入酸溶液调PH值，然后加入硫化铵溶液，除去杂质铁、重金属、稀土等，得到除杂处理后的钙溶液，与氨水、二氧化碳气体进行反应，得到湿体碳酸钙，经清洗所得湿体碳酸钙与氢氟酸反应生成氟化钙，在经低温真空干燥、大气烧结、保温冷却得到高纯紫外氟化钙，本方法制得的氟化钙含杂质量少，纯度高，紫外透过率、激光损伤阈值、单晶口径值、双折射率等满足使用要求。"
                }
